name: PharmacyReasonsForInterventions
title: PharmacyReasonsForInterventions
description: This value set is intended to be used in the Pharmacist eCare Plan.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains a list of reasons for pharmacist interventions completed during a patient encounter.),(Data Element Scope: Datatype Attribute: Reason. Datatype: Intervention. The intent of the terms in this value set is to provide a comprehensive list of issues identified when reviewing a patient's treatment regimen that would prompt further intervention.),(Inclusion Criteria: Any code that represents problems identified that would prompt further pharmacist interventions.),(Exclusion Criteria: Any code that does not represent problems identified that would prompt further interventions.)
